Arduino Build Light

Build light for continuous integration servers, such as Hudson/Jenkins and others to be added soon.

100% open source both hardware and software.

Detailed instructions on how to build and run it:
http://dattein.com/blog/arduino-build-light/


Proudly supported by www.elevenFolders.com

References:
How to setup Java/RXTX to communicate via Serial Port with Arduino: http://silveiraneto.net/2009/03/01/arduino-and-java/
The librxtxSerial.jnilib library for Snow Leopard: http://tech.element77.com/2009/06/arduino-problems-with.html